title: Cafferelli - 16 Extudes for Trumpet.pdf
description:
This is a PDF (Acrobat) e-book of Caferelli's 16 Etudes for Trumpet. These are advanced etudes, similar to those of Theo Charlier. Very well-written, and fine for both pure study and performance. A must for serious students of the trumpet.

This book is now VERY expensive, so I hope this torrent helps out the struggling musician or starving student!

Ready to print at 11.5 x 11. 

Please leave a comment if you would like to have more trumpet books. I have an enormous library already in PDF format, but will only continue to torrent them with genuine interest. There is precious little material like this available as torrents, and it would be nice if trumpet players would share our libraries.
